51

52

53 
 *  set any options such as the constraints field.

55 
 *  @author Dan Klein
56 
 *  @author Christopher Manning (I seem to maintain it....)
57 
 *  @author Jenny Finkel (N-best and sampling code, former from Liang/Chiang)
58 
 */
